name: third_virtue
description:
A suspended memory of
a Lumorian.

name: moblumin_ingot
description:
An ingot of the Moblins' lightweight
 aluminum alloy.

name: moblin_sheepskin
description:
Beautiful curls of fluffy wool adorn
this tough skin.

name: ghrah_m_chip
description:
A smooth piece of tissue taken from
a Luminion known as a ghrah.
A strange light is emitted from its
sparkling center.

name: ancient_beastcoin
description:
A gold coin minted by the Quadav
long ago. Far more ornate than
modern currency, it consists of
nearly pure gold, and a diamond
fitted into its center.

name: skull_locust
description:
This variety of locust has been
devastating Sarutabaruta in recent
years. It is said that mages affixed
the eerie mark resembling a skull to
its head as a prank.

name: mushroom_locust
description:
This variety of locust has adapted
to the jungles of Elshimo. Its unusual
diet consists mainly of mushrooms.

name: snapping_mole
description:
A diminutive variety of mole
that inhabits the Gustaberg region,
snapping moles are very aggressive
and are known to bite miners' ankles.

name: ovinnik_hide
description:
The remarkably glossy
 hide of an ovinnik.

name: catoblepas_hide
description: The stiff hide of a catoblepas.

name: merrow_scale
description:
A pliable, beautiful scale from
a Merrow.

name: apkallu_feather
description: A feather from the wing of an apkallu.

name: colibri_feather
description: A feather from the tail of a colibri.

name: qiqirn_sandbag
description:
The Qiqirn carry these sandbags for
 a quick escape in times of emergency.
 Only a Qiqirn can carry one.

name: lesser_chigoe
description:
A diminutive variety of the Near
Eastern chigoe parasite.

name: qutrub_bandage
description:
One of the bandages that cover the
 qutrubs' entire bodies. It is soaked
 in embalming fluid and an assortment
 of other unappetizing liquids.

name: troll_pauldron
description:
A bronze shoulderpiece from the armor
 of a Troll cannoneer. It is too heavy
 for a person to equip.

name: troll_vambrace
description:
A bronze armpiece from the armor of
a Troll hoplite. It is too heavy for
a person to equip.

name: mamool_ja_helmet
description:
An iron helmet formerly worn by
 a Mamool Ja fighter. Due to its odd
 shape, only Mamool Ja can wear it.

name: pephredo_hive_chip
description:
Part of a hive formed by hardened
pephredo secretions.

name: qutrub_gorget
description:
This gorget once decorated the neck
of a Qutrub. It is too heavy for a
person to equip.

name: lamian_armlet
description:
This armlet once decorated a Lamia's
 wrist. It would not fit on a person.

name: cerberus_claw
description:
A claw from one of Cerberus's paws.
All who gaze upon it are filled with
a sense of dread.
